	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: flash programming with socketted bios</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Egg wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">How do you get the PC to run without its BIOS while you flash the chip?</div><br />MS-DOS and disabling all interrupts.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Also, which type of chip (eprom, eeprom, flash rom) should be used in this case?</div>
<br />The same kind that's in your PC already.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


